      "A survey launched 4 years ago where developers from Morocco ðŸ‡²ðŸ‡¦ tell us about their job satisfaction, salaries, community contribution, how they learn and level up, which tools they're using, how they feel about the Moroccan tech community and what they want to learn next. Check out the the report and learn more.",
